gnat.retrieval
Class GetInfoOnGene

java.lang.Object
  gnat.retrieval.GetInfoOnGene

public class GetInfoOnGene
extends java.lang.Object

Retrieves information on a gene or set of genes with EntrezGene as the hub for background knowledge. Goes from there to GOA and UniProt to collect more data.

Author:
Joerg

URL_ENTREZGENE_XMLDATA

static java.lang.String URL_ENTREZGENE_XMLDATA
The URL to access a gene record in XML format from NCBI eUtils. Simply add the Entrez gene ID (or list of IDs, comma-separated.)

URL_UNIPROT_XMLDATA

static java.lang.String URL_UNIPROT_XMLDATA
URL to access UniProt entries. Add the UniProt ID (P17173) and ".xml".
